{"tid":2209123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢測公司Prenetics與國泰航空10月推出「全球電子健康護照」，國泰香港倫敦希斯洛航綫率先試行","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T13:49:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"375285ba483bf240ad47c8e69db5873087bddb81","tid":2209123,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:50:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2756706/【航空告急】全球電子健康護照10月推出%E3%80%80國泰香港倫敦希斯洛航綫率先試行\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2756706%2F%E3%80%90%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%91%8A%E6%80%A5%E3%80%91%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A710%E6%9C%88%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%25E3%2580%2580%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%B8%8C%E6%96%AF%E6%B4%9B%E8%88%AA%E7%B6%AB%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E8%A9%A6%E8%A1%8C&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=79045826\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2756706/【航空告急】全球電子健康護照10月推出%E3%80%80國泰香港倫敦希斯洛航綫率先試行</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2755000/2756706/tele_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2755000%2F2756706%2Ftele_1024.jpg&h=c3ec9a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n檢測公司Prenetics與國泰航空 （00293） 、健康數據平台的公共信託The Common Projects合作，推行全球電子健康護照，允許旅客透過手機應用程式顯示Prenetics的新冠肺炎病毒測試陰性結果，預計今年10月在香港、倫敦希斯洛機場（Heathrow Airport）航線率先試行。<br />\n<br />\n目前Prenetics於10個國家及地區設有辦公室。阿里巴巴 （09988） 創業基金者基金、平安 （02318） 亦於早期有份投資。截至目前，Prenetics合共通過4輪約6800美元（5.3億港元）融資。<br />\n<br />\n疫情下，Prenetics推出Project Screen by Circle計劃，提供新型冠狀病毒檢測，並負責7月28日至8月24日提供新型冠狀病毒檢測。"},{"pid":"12f322775d43c22cbbd855a8c666958d2db1753f","tid":2209123,"uid":127929,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"我會直接搭英航，piss off la CX"},{"pid":"3fb02c9ada34769a47e2f4a69a4217447dff836c","tid":2209123,"ui